What does it take to give a supercar its unique sound? As you might expect, it's more than just the engine.

Everything has to be considered when engineering a cars' audio character. And for the McLaren Artura, we pushed ourselves to the limit of what was possible with technology today.

The result is a car that has a hugely diverse sound, capable of being scintillating at the top of the rev range, but comfortable while cruising.

How did we do it? Laurence Reucroft, Senior Project Engineer explains...

node.text:
Today, McLaren Automotive and @richardmille unveil our collaborative exclusive RM 40-01 Speedtail timepiece. ​

The watch is limited to just 106 units to match the exclusivity of the 106 Speedtail hypercars handbuilt by McLaren Automotive. 

Each one celebrates the fifth year of our ongoing partnership. #RM4001Speedtail

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McLaren Automotive on July 20, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: The Elva links McLaren’s heritage to its present and future with a name and style that recalls the McLaren-Elva race cars of the 1960’s. These were amongst the first sportscars designed and raced by Bruce McLaren and the company that he founded, and today’s Elva was created to evoke the spirit of driving enjoyment symbolised by these cars. #McLarenElva

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McLaren Automotive on July 19, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: Super-lightweight and extremely powerful, the Elva delivers the ultimate connection between driver, the road and the elements. Winding here through the roads of Scottsdale, Arizona, the Elva was created to celebrate the pure joy of driving. #McLarenElva

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McLaren Automotive on July 17, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
The McLaren GT’s sweeping, sculpted profile isn’t simply our interpretation of what a Grand Tourer can be. But what it should be. Driven by our ‘everything for a reason’ design philosophy. 

#McLarenGT

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McLaren Automotive on July 16, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: In the #McLarenGT carbon fibre passenger cell – unique in the Grand Touring segment – possesses exceptional strength and rigidity while enabling generous interior space and impressive in-car refinement.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by McLaren Automotive on July 16, 2021 tagging @kosten. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: The McLaren GT’s dihedral doors, which are unique in the Grand Touring segment, offer not only a dramatic visual signature when open but have been optimised for use in tight parking spaces, allowing occupants unhindered egress and ingress. #McLarenGT

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McLaren Automotive on July 15, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
The GT is a supercar that is thrilling, yet refined, dynamic and engaging. Never before has a car with such incredible dynamic capabilities been coupled with such class-leading refinement. 

#McLarenGT

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McLaren Automotive on July 15, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: Designed for distance, the #McLarenGT provides the comfort and space expected of a Grand Tourer, but with a level of agility never experienced before in this segment. This is a car that redefines the notion of a Grand Tourer in a way that only a McLaren could.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McLaren Automotive on July 14, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
The McLaren GT combines competition levels of performance with continent-crossing capability.

#McLarenGT

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by McLaren Automotive on July 14, 2021 tagging @kosten. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
Where would your #GTadventure take you?

#McLarenGT

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by McLaren Automotive on July 13, 2021 tagging @kosten. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: Sleek, elegant and muscular, the superlight GT is a compelling blend of beautiful design, high-quality innovative materials and exceptional refinement. #McLarenGT

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by McLaren Automotive on July 13, 2021 tagging @kosten. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
The GT offers the perfect blend of body control and ride comfort. Thrilling handling is balanced with laser-precision straight-line stability. 

#McLaren #McLarenGT
